[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── STALLED-EPISODE DETECTION ────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Detection logic]                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - For each active step in each active episode:       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - Compare actual elapsed time vs. expected         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - Compare actual status vs. expected status        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - Apply episode-template-specific thresholds       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - Detect specific stall patterns:                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │        * Referral sent, not acknowledged                │
